*NB: for each of the involved countries, the worst team in the group pahes is to be replaced for 1999 with the national champions in 1998: Independiente (Argentina), Corinthians (Brazil), Universidad de Chile (Chile), Cerro Porteño (Paraguay) and Peñarol (Uruguay) are the teams "relegated" by this rule.  Since in all cases the 1998 champions were already among the 20 'elect' clubs, no team was actually replaced (Corinthians in fact replace themselves as Brazilian champions 1998).

